message.distributionDefaultInviterIdTip.message: The user ID of the default inviter. If the distribution link does not carry the inviter_id parameter, this user ID will be used as the default inviter.

message.distributionForceInviterIdTip.message: The user ID of the force inviter. If this ID is set, it will be used as the inviter regardless of whether the distribution link carries the inviter_id parameter.

message.originTip.message: Site domain, bound to site configuration, and cannot be changed.

message.titleTip.message: Site title, displayed in the browser tab.

message.descriptionTip.message: Site description, located in the site meta information, used for site SEO optimization.

message.logoTip.message: Site logo, displayed at the top of the site menu when the menu bar is expanded.

message.faviconTip.message: Site favicon, displayed in the browser tab.

message.adminsTip.message: Site administrator ID, the user who first creates the site will become the administrator by default, only site administrators can manage the site.

message.adminsTip2.message: You can add or remove administrator IDs here, you can view user IDs at https://auth.acedata.cloud

message.keywordsTip.message: Site keywords, located in the site meta information, used for site SEO optimization.

message.keywordsTip2.message: You can add or remove website keywords here, the more precise the keywords, the more beneficial for SEO optimization.

message.featuresI18n.message: Open or close multi-language support, after closing, users can only use the default language.
